    "description": "Infested Lands is an addictive game that takes players to a dangerous world where monsters rule. The player takes on the role of a military man who has been sent to a territory known as the &quot;Infested Lands&quot; to investigate and destroy the monsters that inhabit this territory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387010/extras/38610e964cd7a49c8f382bde17c23f55.poster.avif?t=1682792739\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387010/extras/38610e964cd7a49c8f382bde17c23f55.webm?t=1682792739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387010/extras/38610e964cd7a49c8f382bde17c23f55.mp4?t=1682792739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is a classic TDS shooter where you, as a hired worker, have to go to various locations and complete special tasks, destroying enemies.<br><br>Dressed in a camouflage uniform and armed with a machine gun, the hero will find himself in a dark and exciting atmosphere that will not leave you indifferent. In this world, you need to stay alert and ready to fight at any moment, because monsters can appear at any moment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387010/extras/2e947c5994a963861669b21e5e9cdc25.poster.avif?t=1682792739\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387010/extras/2e947c5994a963861669b21e5e9cdc25.webm?t=1682792739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387010/extras/2e947c5994a963861669b21e5e9cdc25.mp4?t=1682792739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>